column5: See him on the news? Likely flown into an  uninhabited lake in Siberia. Pike, trout and perch. Went into the bucket I wonder if he cleaned them ?

Vlad the impaler spearing pike!     Pike spearing in the local creek was one of the first things we did as teens every spring, would have been in the sixties when I was in high school, March and April was the open season. Not sure when they cancelled it. A few 5 prong spear heads came out of the high school metal shop
